    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and functions as a dependable daily driver for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches, minor paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few permanent stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. Mechanically, the car starts reliably, but the suspension is beginning to feel stiff and will likely need professional attention in the near future. It is a solid, functional choice for anyone needing honest transportation at a reasonable price.",
