    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely pristine inside and out. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives as smooth as the day I bought it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
