    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 high-pressure cast-iron block inline-six. This specimen boasts a linear power band facilitated by six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Mechanically impeccable, it has received proactive rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with zero bushing deflection, delivering the precise turn-in and corner-exit stability this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is an analog masterpiece in showroom condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
