    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2019 Sports Coupe in pristine condition. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained as part of a private collection and has never seen a drop of rain or snow. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal, protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or scratches. Every body panel is original with perfect factory tolerances. \n\nInside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition. The premium Nappa leather seats show no bolster wear, and the interior retains its original factory scent. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. All technology interfaces, including the premium infotainment and digital cluster, function flawlessly without a single pixel out of place. \n\nMechanically, this car is peerless. It features a full, documented service history exclusively through authorized dealerships, with the most recent major service completed just 200 miles ago. It sits on a set of brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires wrapped around immaculate alloy wheels with no curb rash whatsoever. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
