      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, this specimen exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition, offered for the most demanding enthusiast.",
