    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
